QuestData.Title: Assault on The Fel Forge
QuestData.Description:
The Iron Horde is growing stronger each day as their war machines are empowered with fel magic. We have even obtained word that they are constructing a Fel Reaver!
Head to the Fel Forge and destroy their forces before we are overwhelmed.
QuestData.LogDescription: Assault the Iron Horde forces at the Fel Forge in Tanaan Jungle.

Objectives.Objective: Assault the Iron Horde forces at the Fel Forge
